with 'getType' you can access the node's type. A Nim type is mapped to a Nim AST too, so it's slightly confusing but it means the same API can be used to traverse types. Recursive types are flattened for you so there is no danger of infinite recursions during traversal. To resolve recursive types, you have to call 'getType' again. To see what kind of type it is, call typeKind on getType's result.
trans-unit.target: 使用“ getType”，您可以访问节点的类型。 Nim类型也映射到Nim AST，因此有点混乱，但这意味着可以使用相同的API遍历类型。递归类型为您扁平化，因此遍历期间没有无限递归的危险。要解析递归类型，您必须再次调用“ getType”。要查看它是哪种类型，请对getType的结果调用typeKind。

trans-unit.source: with this hook you can influence exception handling on a global level. If not nil, every 'raise' statement ends up calling this hook. Ordinary application code should never set this hook! You better know what you do when setting this. If globalRaiseHook returns false, the exception is caught and does not propagate further through the call stack.
trans-unit.target: 使用此挂钩，您可以在全局级别上影响异常处理。如果不为零，则每个“ raise”语句最终都会调用此钩子。普通的应用程序代码永远不要设置此钩子！您最好知道在进行此设置时的操作。如果 globalRaiseHook 返回false，则捕获异常，并且不会通过调用堆栈进一步传播该异常。

trans-unit.source: with this hook you can influence exception handling on a thread local level. If not nil, every 'raise' statement ends up calling this hook. Ordinary application code should never set this hook! You better know what you do when setting this. If localRaiseHook returns false, the exception is caught and does not propagate further through the call stack.
trans-unit.target: 使用此挂钩，您可以在线程本地级别上影响异常处理。如果不为零，则每个“ raise”语句最终都会调用此钩子。普通的应用程序代码永远不要设置此钩子！您最好知道在进行此设置时的操作。如果 localRaiseHook 返回false，则捕获异常，并且不会通过调用堆栈进一步传播。
